##### Bitfield Operations
Order of operations matters for register allocation:
```c
// May use different registers depending on ordering
flags &= (AOBJ_LOOP | AOBJ_NO_UPDATE);
aobj->flags = aobj->flags & ~(flags);

// vs
aobj->flags &= ~(flags & (AOBJ_LOOP | AOBJ_NO_UPDATE));
```
